cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.NE, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with denoising of light field images using convolutional neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves analysis of parallax features, which falls under the category of graphics (cs.GR). The use of neural networks for denoising can also be categorized under machine learning (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE). Lastly, the paper involves extensive experiments and evaluation of the proposed method, which can be categorized under learning (cs.LG).
